      <title>智利总统在新改革推动前因不满情绪上升而感到刺痛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/chile-s-boric-stung-by-rising-disapproval-ahead-of-reform-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据两项新的民意调查，智利总统加布里埃尔·博里奇的支持率在二月底有所上升，突显了他的政府在准备再次推进关键改革时所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/chile-s-boric-stung-by-rising-disapproval-ahead-of-reform-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
