    <item>
      <title>美国在国际货币基金组织访问之前对埃塞俄比亚侵犯人权行为发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-raises-alarm-over-ethiopian-rights-abuses-before-imf-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对埃塞俄比亚持续侵犯人权的行为表示担忧，这可能会影响该国从多边贷款机构获得资金的能力，国际货币基金组织正准备派代表团前往该国讨论一项重要的救助计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-raises-alarm-over-ethiopian-rights-abuses-before-imf-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰敦促欧盟禁止从俄罗斯和白俄罗斯进口食品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/poland-pushes-eu-to-ban-food-imports-from-russia-and-belarus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克表示，波兰将呼吁欧盟委员会全面禁止从俄罗斯和白俄罗斯进口食品，以加强该地区的安全并保护农民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/poland-pushes-eu-to-ban-food-imports-from-russia-and-belarus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:35:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚承诺提供 13 亿美元刺激东南亚投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/australia-pledges-1-3-billion-to-spur-southeast-asia-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理安东尼·艾博内塞将推出一项 20 亿澳元（13 亿美元）的融资安排，作为推动澳大利亚在东南亚贸易和投资的新一揽子计划的核心内容，在中美经济关系存在不确定性的情况下加强区域关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/australia-pledges-1-3-billion-to-spur-southeast-asia-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特准备提高商务航空旅行税以资助预算赠品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jeremy-hunt-prepares-to-hike-business-air-travel-taxes-in-uk-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特正在考虑提高商务旅行的航空旅客税，作为一项潜在的增收措施，以帮助支付周三预算中的个人减税费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jeremy-hunt-prepares-to-hike-business-air-travel-taxes-in-uk-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
