      <title>希腊在强劲需求后出售比雷埃夫斯银行的全部股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/greece-may-sell-entire-stake-in-piraeus-bank-as-offer-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊将出售其所持比雷埃夫斯银行 27% 的全部股份，突显出政府随着经济复苏而剥离其金融资产的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/greece-may-sell-entire-stake-in-piraeus-bank-as-offer-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 21:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院可能周一对特朗普的投票资格做出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/supreme-court-to-issue-opinion-monday-with-ballot-case-pending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院暗示，它可能会在周一就禁止唐纳德·特朗普参加科罗拉多州总统选举投票的努力做出裁决，并在选民准备前往科罗拉多州投票之际，在其日历中增加一个新的意见日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/supreme-court-to-issue-opinion-monday-with-ballot-case-pending</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 18:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
